
Climate change refers to long-term shifts in temperatures and weather patterns. 

The rapid climate change we are now seeing is caused by humans using oil, gas and coal for their homes, factories and transport.  carbon(iv)oxide , sulphur(iv)oxide and the methane are the drivers of climate change.

we can save our climate by burning refuse in incerators , using petroleum product without methyl mercaptan and sulphur(iv)oxide
